#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:5
msgid "Smoothing"
msgstr "平滑"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:8
msgid "Edge Split Modifier"
msgstr "拆边修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:10
msgid ""
"With the :doc:`Edge Split Modifier </modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>`  a result similar to *Auto "
"Smooth* can be achieved with the ability to choose which edges should be split, based on angle. Those "
"Angles are marked as sharp."
msgstr ""
"使用 :doc:`拆边修改器 </modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>` 可以通过基于夹角选择需要分离的边线，实现类"
"似 *自动光滑* 的效果。这些夹角可以标记为锐边。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:19
msgid "Edge Split Modifier enabled, based on angle."
msgstr "基于角度的拆边修改器。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:24
msgid "Edges marked as sharp."
msgstr "标记边线为锐边。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:29
msgid "Resulting render with sharp edge weighting."
msgstr "带有锐边权重的渲染结果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:33
msgid "Smoothing the Mesh Geometry"
msgstr "光滑网格几何结构"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:35
msgid ""
"The above techniques do not alter the mesh itself, only the way it is displayed and rendered. Instead of "
"just making the mesh look like a smooth surface, you can also physically smooth the geometry of the mesh "
"with these tools:"
msgstr ""
"上面的技巧只是调整了网格显示和渲染的方式，而不改变网格本身。不同于仅仅让网格看起来是光滑表面，使用以下工具"
"可以本质上平滑网格的几何结构:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:41
msgid "Mesh Editing Tools"
msgstr "网格编辑工具"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:43
msgid "You can apply one of the following in *Edit Mode*:"
msgstr "可以在 *编辑模式* 下使用以下工具:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:45
msgid ":doc:`Smooth </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`平滑 </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:46
msgid "This relaxes selected components, resulting in a smoother mesh."
msgstr "松弛选中元素，产生平滑的网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:47
msgid ":doc:`Laplacian Smooth </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`拉普拉斯平滑 </modeling/meshes/editing/transform/smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:48
msgid "Smooths geometry by offers controls for better preserving larger details."
msgstr "平滑几何结构，提供控制选项以更好地保留大的细节。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:50
msgid ":doc:`Subdivide Smooth </modeling/meshes/editing/subdividing/subdivide>`"
msgstr ":doc:`平滑细分 </modeling/meshes/editing/subdividing/subdivide>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:50
msgid ""
"Adjusting the *smooth* parameter after using the *subdivide* tool results in a more organic shape. This is "
"similar to using the Subdivision Surface Modifier."
msgstr "在使用 *细分* 工具后调整 *平滑度* 参数，产生更加自然的形状。该工具与表面细分修改器类似。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:54
msgid ":doc:`Bevel </modeling/meshes/editing/introduction>`"
msgstr ":doc:`倒角 </modeling/meshes/editing/introduction>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:53
msgid "This Bevels selected edged, causing sharp edges to be flattened."
msgstr "对选中边倒角，使尖锐的边线更加圆滑。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:57
msgid "Modifiers"
msgstr "修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:59
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can smooth the mesh non-destructively with one or several of the following modifiers:"
msgstr "另外，还可以使用一个或多个下面的修改器，非破坏性的平滑网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:63
msgid ":doc:`Smooth Modifier </modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`平滑修改器 </modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:63
msgid ""
"Works like the *Smooth* tool in *Edit Mode*; can be applied to specific parts of the mesh using vertex "
"groups."
msgstr "与编辑模式下的 *平滑* 工具类似，可以使用顶点组作用于网格的指定部分。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:66
msgid ":doc:`Laplactian Smooth Modifier </modeling/modifiers/deform/laplacian_smooth>`"
msgstr ":doc:`拉普拉斯平滑修改器 </modeling/modifiers/deform/laplacian_smooth>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:66
msgid ""
"Works like the *Laplacian Smooth* tool in *Edit Mode*; can be applied to specific parts of the mesh using "
"vertex groups."
msgstr "与 *编辑模式* 下的 *拉普拉斯平滑* 类似，可以使用顶点组作用于网格的指定部分。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:69
msgid ":doc:`Bevel Modifier </modeling/modifiers/generate/bevel>`"
msgstr ":doc:`倒角修改器 </modeling/modifiers/generate/bevel>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:69
msgid ""
"Works like the *Bevel* tool in *Edit Mode*; Bevel can be set to work on an angle threshold, or on edge "
"weight values."
msgstr "与 *编辑模式* 下的 *倒角* 工具类似，可以设置为基于角度阈值，或边倒角权重。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:76
msgid ":doc:`Subdivision Surface Modifier </modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>`"
msgstr ":doc:`表面细分修改器 </modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:72
msgid ""
"Catmull-Clark subdivision produces smooth results. Sharp edges can be defined with :ref:`subdivision "
"creases <modifiers-generate-subsurf-creases>` or by setting certain edges to \"sharp\" and adding an :doc:"
"`Edge Split Modifier </modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>` (set to *From Marked As Sharp*) before the "
"Subdivision Surface Modifier."
msgstr ""
"Catmull-Clark 细分产生光滑的效果。可以使用 :ref:`细分折痕 <modifiers-generate-subsurf-creases>` 或在添加表"
"面细分修改器前设置指定边为 \"锐边\" ，然后添加 :doc:`拆边修改器</modeling/modifiers/generate/edge_split>` "
"(勾选 *锐边*) 来定义锐边。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:78
msgid "Example mesh with *Auto Smooth* enabled."
msgstr "开启 *自动光滑* 的网格范例。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:83
msgid "Subdivision Surface."
msgstr "细分表面。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:88
msgid "Using creased edges, and resulting subdivision artifacts."
msgstr "使用折痕边，产生细分瑕疵。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:93
msgid "Extra edge loops added."
msgstr "添加额外的循环边。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/smoothing.rst:98
msgid "3D View showing creased edges (pink) and added edges loops (yellow)."
msgstr "3D视图下的折痕边(粉色)，和添加的循环边(黄色)。"
